This is The Inferential Programming Language Interpreter v. 2.0
programmed in Standard ML.

You require Edinburgh Standard ML Core Language compiler v. 4.0
to use this program. In ipl/src directory you find shell
script "make-all". Edit it and run it. Then edit shell script
"ipl" placed in your default directory for binaries.

You can get Edinburgh SML from anonymous ftp at ftp.dcs.ed.ac.uk,
directory export/edml.
